p.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/144292i1C7FB210D6D1A8B2/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_2-1722352766791.png" alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_2-1722352766791.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This is the first time i am working on this MDG. Can anyone help on this as how to get it processed via inbound or any pointers. I was trying to check the standard SAP configuration and didnt find any configuration related to the inbound configuration.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Tirthankar&lt;/P&gt;</content>
